data.description: This one level brick ranch is located on the north side of town close to shopping, banks and restaurants. Great established neighborhood with mature trees and would fit the first time buyers or retired. The house has three bedrooms with one full and one half bath, hardwood floors, a large den with a fireplace that is open to the kitchen and dining area. A screened in covered porch is in the large backyard along with a storage building. This house has been owned by the same family since it was built.
